    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a functional, budget-friendly option for someone looking for reliable transportation. While the engine and transmission are operational, the car shows clear signs of its age, including some noticeable scratches and minor dings on the exterior. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and visible wear from regular use. There are a few minor mechanical items that may require attention soon, such as a worn belt and aging tires, but the car starts up and drives fine for daily commuting. It's an honest workhorse that still has plenty of miles left for a buyer who doesn't mind a bit of character and some upcoming maintenance.",
